race.comment: UNCLE ERNEST (1) has a strong record here with six wins and three placings from 13 starts. Scored by 0.8 lengths last time (22.37) in a Grade 5 over 390m at this track. Expected to be in the finish. NO RUPEES (6) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (22.79) last time out at Geelong. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Expected to feature again. SAILAWAY GIN (7) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 0.6 lengths (22.27) behind Paw Estrella at Warrnambool. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Overdue and gets her chance. MARKET BLUE (2) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.
